{{ChallengePage}}
'''Ascendant''' is a [[Challenges|challenge]] in Risk of Rain 2. It is completed by defeating the [[Teleporter#Teleporter Boss|Teleporter Bosses]] after activating 2 [[Shrine of the Mountain|Shrines of the Mountain]].

