== Trivia == * In the Risk of Rain universe, fireworks were banned on Earth after terrorists disguised missiles as fireworks. They were later re-legalized, in 2054.<ref>https://riskofrain.fandom.com/wiki/Bundle_of_Fireworks#Shipping_Details</ref>
