{{EquipmentPage}} The '''Disposable Missile Launcher''' is a [[Ror:Disposable Missile Launcher|returning]] [[Items#Equipment|equipment]] in Risk of Rain 2.
When activated, the player launches a total of 12 missiles that deal 300% damage each.
Each missile has a [[Proc Coefficient|proc coefficient]] of 1.0.
==Notes== * If the player picks up a different equipment or activates {{SkillLink|Retool|MUL-T}} as {{SurvivorLink|MUL-T}} before all 12 missiles have fired, the Missile Launcher will keep firing until the backlog has caught up, potentially allowing for two equipment active at once.
== Lore == {{Lore}}
