{{ItemPage}} The '''{{PAGENAME}}''' is a [[Ror:Leeching Seed|returning]] [[Items|item]] in Risk of Rain 2.
Upon damaging an enemy, the holder recovers 1 (''+1 per stack'') health, multiplied by the [[Proc Coefficient|proc coefficient]] of the hit.
== Notes == * Visuals for damage and healing numbers are rounded up, so the Leeching Seed's healing may appear as 1 per hit when in fact it may be lower. *{{Color|note|Correction:}} Healing is only applied on hit, not on damage.
== Tips == * Shotgun attacks such as {{SurvivorLink|survivorName=Bandit|altText=Bandit's}} {{SkillLink|Burst|Bandit}} and {{SurvivorLink|survivorName=Captain|altText=Captain's}} {{SkillLink|Vulcan Shotgun|Captain}} work well with Leeching Seeds, since each attack fires many individual hits. ** On the other hand, [[Survivors]] with relatively low attack speed or hit count, such as {{SurvivorLink|survivorName=Loader}}, will struggle to make good use of this item.
* This item becomes generally outclassed by the {{ItemLink|Harvester's Scythe}} once the player has enough [[Damage#Critical Strike|critical strike chance]]. *The hit requirement makes it unsuitable for Damage over Time effects such as poison or bleed.
== Lore == {{Lore}}
== Version History == {{VersionHistory| ; [[Anniversary Update]] * Major Content ** Added New Lore Entry: {{PAGENAME}} * Quality of Life ** Update visuals to match other assets }}
== Trivia == * This item is based on the real world [[wikipedia:Orobanche|Broomrape]] plant, which is parasitic.
