{{ChallengePage}} '''Macho''' is a [[Challenges|challenge]] in Risk of Rain 2. It is completed by dealing 5000 [[damage]] in one shot.
==Tip== * Gathering many {{ItemLink|itemName=Crowbar|altText=Crowbars}} to use with [[Survivors]] that have single, strong hits, such as {{SurvivorLink|survivorName=Loader}} or {{SurvivorLink|survivorName=Artificer}}, makes quick work of this challenge. *Using the slamming attack of {{ItemLink|H3AD-5T v2}} is a great way to complete this challenge early in a run. * Activating the {{ItemLink|Charged Perforator}} is a great way to complete this challenge, since it multiplies the damage of the activating hit by 500%. * The {{ItemLink|Royal Capacitor}} easily completes this challenge, with every character having a starting base damage of 11 and higher. * Triggering the {{ItemLink|AtG Missile Mk. 1}} or Charged Perforator using the H3AD-5T v2, {{ItemLink|Will-o'-the-wisp}}, {{ItemLink|Ceremonial Dagger}}, {{ItemLink|N'kuhana's Opinion}} or {{ItemLink|Little Disciple}} will deal a huge amount of damage. * Getting below 25% HP while holding a {{ItemLink|Genesis Loop}} and hitting any enemy with the resulting supernova will instantly complete this challenge.
