{{ItemPage}} The '''{{PAGENAME}}''' is an [[Items|item]] in Risk of Rain 2.
When the holder kills an enemy, the cooldown for their held [[Items#Equipment|equipment]] instantly decreases by 4 seconds (''+2 seconds per stack'').
== Effective limit == The following amount of stacks of Soulbound Catalyst is needed to instantly recharge equipment on kill.
