== Notes == * The {{ItemLink|Fuel Array}}, {{ItemLink|The Crowdfunder}}, {{ItemLink|Executive Card}}, and the Elite Equipment do not have cooldowns, and thus do not benefit from {{PAGENAME}}. * Destroying clay pots or barrels will count towards the cooldown reduction. * Kills scored by {{SurvivorLink|Engineer|Engineer's}} {{SkillLink|TR12 Gauss Auto-Turret|Engineer|Turrets}} will not reduce Engineer's equipment cooldown. * Using this item with the {{ItemLink|Forgive Me Please}} reduces its cooldown by a total of 32 seconds over a period of 8 seconds. This allows the player to activate the Forgive Me Please equipment every 5 seconds.
